OL,3,CHistoric Grade-II listed pub reopens
OL,4,Cafter being saved by local community
OL,6,FAn historic pub near Bath that dates
OL,7,Fback almost 500 years has finally
OL,8,Freopened after a mammoth community
OL,9,Feffort.
OL,11,FWork to open the Hop Pole Inn at
OL,12,FLimpley Stoke has taken almost three
OL,13,Fyears. Hundreds of people donated more
OL,14,Fthan a million pounds and volunteered
OL,15,Fcountless hours to painstakingly
OL,16,Frestore it to its former glory.
