OL,3,CHistoric Grade-II listed pub reopens
OL,4,Cafter being saved by local community
OL,6,FThe Hop Pole Inn has been serving
OL,7,Fdrinks since 1580 but closed down in
OL,8,F2018 and was due to be sold to
OL,9,Fdevelopers so it could be turned into
OL,10,Fhousing.
OL,12,FBut it was bought by the community
OL,13,Finstead in 2022, in the first of what
OL,14,Fhas become a series of marathon
OL,15,Ffundraising events.
OL,17,FWhen members of the Save The Hop Pole
OL,18,Fcampaign group first entered their new
OL,19,Fpurchase, they found rotten beams, a
OL,20,Fhole in the roof, broken electrics and
OL,21,Flots of damp.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
