OL,3,CHistoric Grade-II listed pub reopens
OL,4,Cafter being saved by local community
OL,6,FIt led to another fundraising drive to
OL,7,Fpay for the vital repairs needed to
OL,8,Fturn it from a literal building site
OL,9,Finto a functional pub.
OL,11,FIn all, the group needed to raise a
OL,12,Fmillion pounds, on top of the #360,000
OL,13,Fthey had first collected to buy the
OL,14,Fsite. They managed to gather more than
OL,15,Fhalf the money through selling shares
OL,16,Fin the Hope Pole Inn, but turned to
OL,17,F'scrounging' the local area for
OL,18,Fbuilding materials.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
