OL,3,CHistoric Grade-II listed pub reopens
OL,4,Cafter being saved by local community
OL,6,F'The community has turned a dream into
OL,7,Fthe reality that is the Hop Pole Inn
OL,8,Ftoday'
OL,10,FThe Hop Pole Inn held a special
OL,11,Fceremony at 4pm on Saturday 25 January
OL,12,F2025 to mark the long-awaited occasion
OL,13,F- officially reopening to the public.
OL,15,FSimon Coombe said: "When we bought
OL,16,Fthis building, we were excited but it
OL,17,Fwas an absolute wreck. It should have
OL,18,Fprobably been pulled down. The walls
OL,19,Fwere falling down, the water was
OL,20,Fdripping through the roof, and that's
OL,21,Fwhen our real work started."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
