OL,3,CHistoric Grade-II listed pub reopens
OL,4,Cafter being saved by local community
OL,6,FHannah Randall, one of the inn's new
OL,7,Flandlords, told ITV West Country she
OL,8,Fand fellow landlord Charlie have been
OL,9,F"welcomed with open arms".
OL,11,F"We're just so excited. We have had a
OL,12,Fhuge amount of support", she added.
